 Hundred Years' War","description":"The Hundred Years' War between France and England was largely due to the question of legitimate succession to the French crown.","jurisdictionLevel":2}],"lifeSummary":"When William de Ingoldesthorpe was born in 1316, in Norfolk, England, his father, Sir John Ingoldsthorpe II, was 22 and his mother, Joan de Weyland, was 17. He married Eleanor Hastings before 1372, in Cambridgeshire, England, United Kingdom. They were the parents of at least 1 son. He died in 1372, in Ingoldisthorpe, Norfolk, England, at the age of 56."},"et":{"1316–1372":"1316–1372","1313–1337":"1313–1337","1325–1371":"1325–1371","1361–1420":"1361–1420","1294–1335":"1294–1335","1300–1342":"1300–1342","12 December 1371":"12. detsember 1371","1361":"1361","1372":"1372","1294":"1294","1371":"1371","1316":"1316","1337":"1337","1325":"1325","1335":"1335","1313":"1313","1300":"1300","1453":"1453","1420":"1420","1342":"1342","before 1372":"enne 1372","1328":"1328","Bourough Green, Cambridgeshire,England":"Cambridgeshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Ingoldisthorpe, Norfolk, England":"Ingoldisthorpe, Norfolk, England","Norfolk, England":"Norfolk, England","Rainham, Essex, England":"Rainham, Essex, England"},"fi":{"1316–1372":"1316–1372","1313–1337":"1313–1337","1325–1371":"1325–1371","1361–1420":"1361–1420","1294–1335":"1294–1335","1300–1342":"1300–1342","12 December 1371":"12. joulukuuta 1371","1361":"1361","1372":"1372","1294":"1294","1371":"1371","1316":"1316","1337":"1337","1325":"1325","1335":"1335","1313":"1313","1300":"1300","1453":"1453","1420":"1420","1342":"1342","before 1372":"ennen vuotta 1372","1328":"1328","Bourough Green, Cambridgeshire,England":"Cambridgeshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Ingoldisthorpe, Norfolk, England":"Ingoldisthorpe, Norfolk, England","Norfolk, England":"Norfolk, England","Rainham, Essex, England":"Rainham, Essex, England"},"fr":{"1316–1372":"1316–1372","1313–1337":"1313–1337","1325–1371":"1325–1371","1361–1420":"1361–1420","12